2017年12月，日本横田空军基地对新型C-130J进行了训练，并首次与日本空中自卫队、澳大利亚皇家空军和菲律宾空军进行了四方演习。

为了应对COVID-19大流行，密克罗尼西亚总统[[戴维·帕努埃洛|戴维·帕努埃洛]]选择在2020年退出第69次圣诞行动。<ref>{{cite web |title=Federated States of Micronesia opts out of annual US military humanitarian mission due to Covid-19 concerns |url=https://www.rnz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/432131/federated-states-of-micronesia-opts-out-of-annual-us-military-humanitarian-mission-due-to-covid-19-concerns |website=RNZ |access-date=4 December 2020 |language=en-nz |date=4 December 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221190749/https://www.rnz.co.nz/international/pacific-news/432131/federated-states-of-micronesia-opts-out-of-annual-us-military-humanitarian-mission-due-to-covid-19-concerns |dead-url=no }}</ref>据军士长安东尼·比耶勒介绍，飞机将按计划继续降落在帕劳共和国，美国空军已采取广泛措施防止新冠病毒传播。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Lloyd |first1=Bruce |title=Operation Christmas Drop isn't canceled |url=https://www.guampdn.com/story/news/local/2020/12/01/operation-christmas-drop-guam-isnt-canceled/3789614001/ |website=Pacific Daily News |access-date=4 December 2020}}</ref>

